        "subject": "LU-5735 mdt: add missing reconstructors for opcodes",
        "message": "LU-5735 mdt: add missing reconstructors for opcodes\n\nSome opcodes (REINT_RMENTRY, REINT_MIGRATE) don't have\nreconstructors, which might cause NUll pointer derefernce when\nresent RPCs are beinh handled.\n\nThis patch adds the reconstructors, and also adds some checking\ncodes for it.\n\nSigned-off-by: Li Xi <lixi@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: Ifcf7a066e29a33c23a3fdd9b14837c2c568b5920\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
